@startuml
' --- 時序圖 (Cryptocurrency Analysis System) ---



== 1. 匯率計算階段 (Exchange Calculator) ==

User -> App: 選擇 1. 匯率計算
activate App

loop 直到輸入 exit
    User -> App: 輸入目標幣種 (如: POL) 與台幣金額
    
    App -> Rate: getTwdToUsdtFromBitoPro()
    activate Rate
    Rate -> Http: get(BitoPro_URL)
    Http -> API: Request (USDT/TWD)
    API --> Http: JSON Data
    Http --> Rate: JSON String
    Rate -> Rate: 解析 lastPrice 並倒數
    Rate --> App: 回傳 TWD->USDT 匯率
    deactivate Rate

    App -> Rate: getUsdtToCryptoFromBitget(symbol)
    activate Rate
    Rate -> Http: get(Bitget_URL)
    Http -> API: Request (Target/USDT)
    API --> Http: JSON Data
    Http --> Rate: JSON String
    Rate -> Rate: 解析 lastPr 並倒數
    Rate --> App: 回傳 USDT->Target 匯率
    deactivate Rate

    App -> User: 提示輸入手續費 (BitoPro/Bitget)
    User -> App: 輸入數值或按 Enter (預設)
    
    App -> App: 計算扣費後最終獲得量
    App -> User: 顯示報價、手續費與計算結果
end
deactivate App

== 2. 網格排行階段 (Grid Ranker) ==

User -> App: 選擇 2. 網格成績排行
activate App

loop 幣種清單編輯
    User -> App: 輸入 [+幣種] 或 [-幣種]
end
User -> App: 按 Enter 開始分析

loop 對於清單中每個幣種
    App -> Grid: analyze(symbol)
    activate Grid
    
    Grid -> Http: get(Binance_Klines_URL)
    Http -> API: Request (K-lines 1d, limit 50)
    API --> Http: JSON Array
    Http --> Grid: JSON String
    
    Grid -> Grid: 解析 K 線數據 (Open/High/Low/Close/Vol)
    
    Grid -> Indicator: calculateMA / calculateActualADX / calculateATRPercent
    activate Indicator
    Indicator --> Grid: 回傳技術指標數值
    deactivate Indicator
    
    Grid -> Indicator: calculateRankingScore(MarketData)
    activate Indicator
    Indicator -> Indicator: 根據權重 (A組趨勢, B組波動) 評分
    Indicator --> Grid: 回傳總分 (Score)
    deactivate Indicator
    
    Grid --> App: 返回封裝好的 MarketData 物件
    deactivate Grid
end

App -> App: 依據 Score 進行降冪排序

App -> Report: printConsoleTable(results)
activate Report
Report --> User: 顯示格式化表格 (排名/幣種/得分/趨勢)
deactivate Report

App -> Report: saveToTxt(results)
activate Report
Report -> Report: 生成檔名 (Grid_Rank_時間.txt)
Report -> LocalFile: 寫入分析報告
Report --> App: 儲存成功通知
deactivate Report

App -> User: 顯示「報告已儲存」提示
deactivate App

@enduml]